T1  - The Impact of New Product Introduction on Plant Productivity in the North American Automotive Industry
AU  - Gopal, Anandasivam
AU  - Goyal, Manu
AU  - Netessine, Serguei
AU  - Reindorp, Matthew
Y1  - 2013/05/07
PY  - 2013
DA  - 2013/10/01
